               <head>Collection of astronomical works</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85009019" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Astronomical works.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="20r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">Al-Aḥdab, Iṣḥak ben Shlomo</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">חדב, יצחק בן שלמה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Kele ḥemdah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">כלי חמדה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Folios 1-10 contain a number of notes and excerpts on philosophical and mathematical topics, apparently in the handwriting of Mordekhai Comtino (15th century), whose signature is found on folio 7v. Al-Aḥdab's treatise begins on folio 11r. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">Al-Aḥdab, Iṣḥak ben Shlomo</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/61397975">חדב, יצחק בן שלמה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Oraḥ selulah</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ארח סלולה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="20v" to="39v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A long introduction precedes the tables (folios 20v-32r). </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="40r" to="48v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ḥibur ῾al ha-luaḥ</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">חבור על הלוח</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/315202793">Isaac ben Elijah, ha-Kohen</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/315202793">יצחק בן אליהו הכהן</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A short astronomical treatise, with the tables of the latitude of Syracuse in Sicily. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="49r" to="119v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/81287">Abraham bar Hiyya Savasorda</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/81287">אברהם בן חייא</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Tsurat ha-arets</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">צורת הארץ</title>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="120r" to="121v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Ha-mevaḳesh</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">המבקש</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/71428967">Falaquera, Shem Tov ben Joseph</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/71428967">פלקירא, שם טוב בן יוסף אבן</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>A fragment only, written in an Oriental semi-cursive script of the 17th century. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="122r" to="129v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="en">Fragments of astronomical and astrological works</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">קטעים מחבורים באסטרונומיה ואסטרולוגיה</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Fragments, written in Sefardi semi-cursive script of probably 14th century. Folios 123-128 are occupied with circular diagrams of the zodiac, accompanied by notes. Folio 129 contains a list of designations and a circular diagram, accompanied by an explanation in Arabic.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
